{"id":164703,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/灌水闲话几个警句/","date":"2011-06-30T06:00:05Z","modified":"2011-06-30T08:57:50Z","title":"[灌水]闲话几个警句","content":"<div><span><a href=\"http://user.kdnet.net/index.asp?userid=1906407\">六月凉开水</a></span> 于 2011/6/30 11:20:40 发布在 <span><a href=\"http://club.kdnet.net\">凯迪社区</a> &gt; <a href=\"http://club.kdnet.net/list.asp?boardid=5\">原创文学</a></span></div>\n<div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>1、<span> </span></span><span>输要输得像个英雄，死要死得像个烈士；</span></p>\n<p><span>2、<span> </span></span><span>人员流失就像放血，开始没什么感觉，最后却会要命；</span></p>\n<p><span>3、<span> </span></span><span>一个坏的团队，能把一个好主意运作的一塌糊涂；</span></p>\n<p><span>4、<span> </span></span><span>善谋者不战，善战者不败，善败者不乱；</span></p>\n<p><span>5、<span> </span></span><span>必要的时候，要有壮士断臂的气度；</span></p>\n<p><span>6、<span> </span></span><span>不敢说真话是个人的耻辱，不能说真话是社会的耻辱；</span></p>\n<p><span>7、<span> </span></span><span>童年无知可爱，少年无知可笑，青年无知可怜，中年无知可叹，老年无知可悲；</span></p>\n<p><span>8、<span> </span></span><span>当今中国有财富阶层，却无上流社会；</span></p>\n<p><span>9、<span> </span></span><span>有钱者无耻，有力者无能，有能者无事，有事者无用；</span></p>\n<p><span>10、<span> </span></span> <span>大国手门下，只能出二国手，二国手门下却可以出大国手，无国手的时代，只能出奴才。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>（读书札记）</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&amp;ip=1&amp;img=1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a></p></form>\n","author":1,"categories":[20534],"tags":[]}